# Shora — Luxury Aura Website

This is the Shora prototype website (React + Vite).

## Run Locally
1. Install [Node.js](https://nodejs.org) (v18+)
2. Clone repo and run:
3. Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)

## Notes
- This is frontend-only (demo).  
- For production: connect a backend, add payment gateway, and deploy on Vercel/Netlify.
